metadata.description: Trollz is a collection of 1,000 uniquely hand drawing digital collectibles living on the Ethereum Blockchain. Each Trollz is unique. There are 5 mythical Trollz who have exclusive traits! Ownership of a Trollz gives rewards and access to the Collector Restricted Channel on our Discord server and much more! These Gen-X Trollz are the first step towards breeding a Gen-Z (X (= Trollz) + Y (= Trollzy) = Z). Owning a Trollz also allows you to take part in the decisions of the project thanks to a voting system. Take part in this growing community! Welcome to you Trollz!
